After battling what he called a spiritual sickness, veteran Nollywood actor, Kayode Odumosu, popularly known as Pa Kasumu is dead.
According to the President of the Theater Arts and Motion Picture Producers Association of Nigeria, Mr Bolaji Amusan, aka Mr Latin, Kasumu died Sunday afternoon.
Pa Kasumu’s health took a dive in 2017 after a medical trip to India.
He would later seek help i churches and Christian leaders like the RCCG General Overseer E.A. Adeboye.
But the late actor said his ailment wasn’t ordinary, denying speculations that his former lifestyle of drinking and smoking was responsible.
 

			
